=================================
|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME |
---------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP SEMI JOIN |     |
|1 |├─TABLE GET           |A(i1)|
|2 |└─SUBPLAN SCAN        |VIEW1|
|3 |  └─TABLE GET         |B(i1)|
=================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([A.c1], [A.c2], [A.c3]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      conds([A.c2 = VIEW1.B.c2 OR A.c3 = VIEW1.B.c3]), nl_params_(nil), use_batch=false
  1 - output([A.c2], [A.c3], [A.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([A.__pk_increment], [A.c2], [A.c3], [A.c1]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=true, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([A.c1], [A.shadow_pk_0]), range[1,NULL ; 1,NULL], 
      range_cond([A.c1 = 1])
  2 - output([VIEW1.B.c2], [VIEW1.B.c3]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([VIEW1.B.c2], [VIEW1.B.c3])
  3 - output([B.c2], [B.c3]), filter(nil), rowset=16
      access([B.__pk_increment], [B.c2], [B.c3]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=true, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([B.c1], [B.shadow_pk_0]), range[1,NULL ; 1,NULL], 
      range_cond([B.c1 = 1])
select /*+no_semi_to_inner no_expand*/ * from t1 A where exists (select 1 from t1 B where (A.c2 = B.c2 or A.c3 = B.c3) and c1 = 1) and c1 = 1;
