================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                             |NAME |
------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN           |     |
|1 |├─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN         |     |
|2 |│ ├─TABLE RANGE SCAN                 |a    |
|3 |│ └─MATERIAL                         |     |
|4 |│   └─SUBPLAN SCAN                   |VIEW1|
|5 |│     └─LIMIT                        |     |
|6 |│       └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |     |
|7 |│         ├─SUBPLAN SCAN             |VIEW3|
|8 |│         │ └─TABLE GET              |d    |
|9 |│         └─SUBPLAN SCAN             |VIEW2|
|10|│           └─TABLE RANGE SCAN       |c    |
|11|└─MATERIAL                           |     |
|12|  └─TABLE GET                        |b    |
================================================
